---
title: Mirage Canopy Blog
author: Camels
---

This is a small MirageOS webservice, using [canopy](https://github.com/Engil/Canopy).
Feel free to add content (by creating a file in [this repository](https://github.com/mirage/canopy-data)).


**[Posts](http://canopy.mirage.io/Posts)**

Progress reports on specific projects, feature sets and Mirage and Unikernel events.

**[Projects](http://canopy.mirage.io/Projects)**

Mirage Pioneer Projects are listed here, with resources, mentors and difficulty/experience ratings.

**[IRC Logs](http://canopy.mirage.io/irclogs)**

Each fortnightly Mirage catch-up is logged on IRC and pushed here.
